1
00:00:06,100 --> 00:00:09,930
♪I waited through spring rain,
summer heat♪

2
00:00:10,560 --> 00:00:13,780
♪Autumn leaves, and winter frost♪

3
00:00:14,190 --> 00:00:16,900
♪But I never got to be with you♪

4
00:00:16,900 --> 00:00:21,340
♪To plant flowers
across all four seasons♪

5
00:00:21,530 --> 00:00:25,480
♪I watched sunsets blend into the night♪

6
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:29,230
♪Waited as the moon drifted,
Milky Way shifted♪

7
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:32,200
♪Still, I never stayed with you♪

8
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:35,820
♪Through the dark,
seeing a world so bright♪

9
00:00:35,820 --> 00:00:37,980
=The Secret Contract of the Witch=

10
00:00:38,020 --> 00:00:40,980
=Episode 22=

11
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:42,560
I'll cut the brisket like this.

12
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:47,880
Chop the tomato into pieces first.

13
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,190
Wait, that's not right.

14
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:52,880
Don't cut it yet.

15
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:54,720
You need to peel it first.

16
00:00:55,930 --> 00:00:59,460
♪When the day stops♪

17
00:00:59,780 --> 00:01:03,180
♪We'll play our favorite songs♪

18
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:06,990
♪With heart and soul♪

19
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:11,810
♪Dancing with the moon♪

20
00:01:12,910 --> 00:01:16,920
♪When my dreams get so hazy♪

21
00:01:17,210 --> 00:01:20,650
♪And sky becomes gray♪

22
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:27,870
♪You'll be the one to guide♪

23
00:01:33,930 --> 00:01:37,290
♪On nights when I can't sleep♪

24
00:01:37,610 --> 00:01:41,050
♪Loneliness fills my heart♪

25
00:01:41,690 --> 00:01:44,770
♪Lost in restless thoughts alone♪

26
00:01:48,410 --> 00:01:51,810
♪The moonlight shines down the hall♪

27
00:01:51,810 --> 00:01:53,610
♪Like a land of tender solace♪

28
00:01:55,570 --> 00:01:59,090
♪But I can't catch the light♪

29
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,200
When will the shooting stars show up?

30
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,720
They said in about half an hour.

31
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,320
That's the best time to watch.

32
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:08,700
That's a long wait.

33
00:02:12,740 --> 00:02:14,340
Catching shooting stars is tough.

34
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:18,780
Couples everywhere are waiting too.

35
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:21,340
Do you think they wait like this?

36
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:27,220
Or maybe they wait holding each other?

37
00:02:27,330 --> 00:02:29,970
♪I keep that look close to my heart♪

38
00:02:30,090 --> 00:02:33,610
♪If you happen to look at the moon too♪

39
00:02:33,930 --> 00:02:37,230
♪Let the moon say what I wish to tell you♪

40
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,340
Now that's more like it.

41
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:42,620
A meteor shower is really romantic.

42
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:46,580
I want you to feel it too.

43
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:48,140
That kind of passionate love.

44
00:02:49,580 --> 00:02:52,140
But not every love needs to be intense.

45
00:02:55,220 --> 00:02:57,420
I think what we have now is perfect.

46
00:02:57,490 --> 00:03:00,680
♪You're the one who shines the brightest♪

47
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,560
No,

48
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:05,740
I just want to give you the best things

49
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:06,620
in the world.

50
00:03:07,940 --> 00:03:09,060
So you can be even happier,

51
00:03:10,460 --> 00:03:11,340
and smile even more.

52
00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:17,140
♪When I struggle so hard alone♪

53
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:18,620
A shooting star.

54
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:20,620
Where is it?

55
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:24,660
♪The grown-up world feels so tense♪

56
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:31,660
♪Then you show up by my side♪

57
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:33,980
♪Stay with me through thick and thin♪

58
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:37,900
♪Your eyes hold a steady gaze♪

59
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:40,860
♪I keep that look close to my heart♪

60
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:44,500
♪If you happen to look at the moon too♪

61
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:48,300
♪Let the moon say what I wish to tell you♪

62
00:03:48,540 --> 00:03:51,860
♪All those simple moments we share♪

63
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:55,300
♪Are honestly all I ever wish for♪

64
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:58,360
♪If you happen to look at the moon too♪

65
00:03:58,390 --> 00:03:59,360
Sorry about that.

66
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:01,980
You didn't get to see a shooting star.

67
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:04,220
It's not your fault.

68
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:05,980
The clouds are just too thick.

69
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:09,420
We can try again next time.

70
00:04:11,380 --> 00:04:13,700
I just don't know when that'll be.

71
00:04:16,740 --> 00:04:17,620
Maybe next year.

72
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:21,780
Or maybe even now.

73
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:26,030
♪If you happen to look at the moon too♪

74
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:27,820
Look, a shooting star. Make a wish.

75
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:32,620
Mu Hanyu.

76
00:04:33,780 --> 00:04:35,140
I hope from now on,

77
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,700
you eat well,

78
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:39,260
sleep tight,

79
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,060
and take care of yourself.

80
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:44,320
♪Please remember how the Milky Way burns♪

81
00:04:44,340 --> 00:04:45,220
Xia Mo,

82
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:47,540
I hope

83
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:49,960
♪In this endless sea of people♪

84
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,500
we can always stay together.

85
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:53,940
Mu Hanyu,

86
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:55,900
meeting you

87
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:59,900
has been the best thing for me.

88
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:03,220
I hope from now on,

89
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:06,300
you keep chasing your dreams

90
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:09,340
and leave the sadness behind.

91
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:21,420
(Lane 66)

92
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:56,540
Xinyi.

93
00:05:59,700 --> 00:06:00,620
Xinyi.

94
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:04,300
Xinyi.

95
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:10,700
Gone again?

96
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:19,980
Xinyi!

97
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:26,300
(Lane 66)

98
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:27,180
Xinyi.

99
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,580
I know you're here.

100
00:06:30,740 --> 00:06:32,220
Xinyi, come out now.

101
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:33,980
No matter what comes our way,

102
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,300
we'll face it together.

103
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:36,980
(Lane 66)

104
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:37,860
Don't be scared.

105
00:06:38,170 --> 00:06:40,020
I'll shoulder this with you, okay?

106
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:43,300
Xinyi,

107
00:06:44,580 --> 00:06:45,860
I'll wait for you to come home.

108
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:55,900
(Mo, I know I was wrong.)

109
00:06:56,580 --> 00:06:58,500
(I need to make up for what I did.)

110
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:01,460
(Lane 66)

111
00:07:06,660 --> 00:07:09,420
(Mu Hanyu should know that J is still alive.)

112
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:17,460
(Lane 66)

113
00:07:19,660 --> 00:07:20,620
Xia Mo.

114
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:25,340
Xia Mo.

115
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:36,180
(I saw her come in.)

116
00:07:39,460 --> 00:07:40,620
Are you here to see her?

117
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:46,300
Yeah.

118
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:47,460
Is she not here?

119
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:50,620
Don't you usually call her first?

120
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:52,100
She brings you into the bar.

121
00:07:53,260 --> 00:07:54,540
I already reached out to her.

122
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:55,540
She hasn't replied to me.

123
00:07:55,540 --> 00:07:57,260
I came over because I was worried.

124
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:01,620
Even though the rose petals stopped falling,

125
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:04,020
her pain just got worse.

126
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:06,020
She doesn't have much time left.

127
00:08:07,100 --> 00:08:08,060
Rose petals?

128
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:16,980
Oh, right.

129
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:21,260
You were the last one to see him.

130
00:08:22,420 --> 00:08:23,300
He...

131
00:08:24,530 --> 00:08:25,620
Is he really gone?

132
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:31,820
Did he say anything before he died?

133
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:34,900
Did he ever mention me?

134
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:40,860
You care about him a lot.

135
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,380
No.

136
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:45,860
I just want to know.

137
00:08:46,340 --> 00:08:47,860
Was it painful when he died?

138
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,740
Did you want him to suffer,

139
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:52,100
or not suffer at all?

140
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:56,660
Of course, I wanted him to suffer.

141
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:01,660
I hope he suffers when he goes.

142
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:06,860
You hate him that much.

143
00:09:09,380 --> 00:09:10,260
He deserved it.

144
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,060
I know you're worried about Mo.

145
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:17,620
I believe in you.

146
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:20,300
You'll finish the contract and save her.

147
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:21,780
Come on, let's go.

148
00:09:22,620 --> 00:09:23,820
I'll take you into the bar.

149
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:11,580
Xinyi.

150
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:15,060
Hanyu.

151
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,180
What brings you here?

152
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:19,700
I was a bit worried about you.

153
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:20,820
So I came to check on you.

154
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:21,860
Are you alright?

155
00:10:22,820 --> 00:10:23,700
I'm fine, really.

156
00:10:24,020 --> 00:10:25,260
How did you get in?

157
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:29,060
Xinyi helped me get in.

158
00:10:30,340 --> 00:10:31,860
I knew she'd come back.

159
00:10:32,820 --> 00:10:34,620
But she's still avoiding me.

160
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:37,460
She...

161
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:40,300
She actually cares about you.

162
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:42,740
She worries you don't have much time.

163
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,940
She asked me to save you by the contract.

164
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:46,540
As long as you agree,

165
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:48,660
I'm willing.

166
00:10:49,940 --> 00:10:51,300
What's up with you today?

167
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:54,380
Didn't we agree to face this together?

168
00:10:54,380 --> 00:10:55,260
Did you forget?

169
00:10:56,820 --> 00:10:58,060
How could I, babe?

170
00:10:58,500 --> 00:10:59,540
I just want you

171
00:11:00,220 --> 00:11:01,620
to keep living well.

172
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:04,460
Babe?

